responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "E7947C1046AEA57286BACAB6824F17FC", "Well, if you do, you report it to the Watch or any Kaelar Guardsman. This Piper fellow has been a thorn in our back for far too long. No doubt, he\'s involved in the demons that have bloomed in the ancient citadel. Now, move along!")
